{"tid":1156982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［人生贏家］ACO30年後人工達近10萬","createTime":"2019-05-16T03:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T04:10:37.000Z","uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"396a171a61d84ec81cbd66edbf71a083beaf6483","tid":1156982,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"小弟計過ACO人工計埋通漲大概係<br />\n<br />\n用2018年政府薪金表計，ACO起薪14780，15年頂薪30165<br />\n<br />\n但咁唔係最終人工，以過往10年平均通漲令公務員人工升幅係每年平均3.94%<br />\n<br />\n即係30年後，個人工都係會每年keep住加3.9%<br />\n<br />\n咁計完之後，就係92587<br />\n<br />\n而岩岩今年又加3.87%<br />\n<br />\n所以起薪點會變 15352，頂薪31332<br />\n而30年後連通漲人工將會係：96170<br />\n（第31年係99962）<br />\n文員仔十皮野一個月不是夢！<br />\n<br />\n當然條數有好多變數，例如公務員未必年年加薪，可以凍薪甚至減人工<br />\n<br />\n另外，我想講既係<br />\n第30即係2048年<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而香港過唔到2047</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家發下夢算"},{"pid":"cbb726a06a8f6c119c316c5dca607303ab94a263","tid":1156982,"uid":131064,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:09:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">为什麽用非法汉语书写?2047年没有香港，只有一个中国!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b3a12a6d44e283aa22967b2bd9fee9d28ba48f10","tid":1156982,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"ACO過唔到2047嘅機會大啲，定係你份工過唔到嘅機會大啲？"},{"pid":"0e8c427205e83797878eaf45ecc682c303cdc617","tid":1156982,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3a12a6d44e283aa22967b2bd9fee9d28ba48f10","tid":1156982,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"ACO過唔到2047嘅機會大啲，定係你份工過唔到嘅機會大啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"一睇就知我無業遊民，等拎三公"},{"pid":"cd7bab9c4b3b130302792c953e12b5393f452208","tid":1156982,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:17:55.000Z","msg":"Btw<br />\n可能未到2047, 大灣區香港市既公職人員